headline.main: Purdue Knocks Off No. 9 Ohio State 71-60 in Big Ten Semis
headline.print_headline: Purdue Knocks Off No. 9 Ohio State 71-60 in Big Ten Semis

lead_paragraph: Purdue's recipe for an upset in the Big Ten Tournament was simple: exploit a few holes in Ohio State's game, then make some free throws.
